_sText:
Cantina is a relatively small map featuring loads of cover, realistic atmosphere and high standard gameplay. Keep your eyes on the ceiling, you never know when somebody might fall out right in front of you!

The basic concept was done after about 2 days, patches stretch the development time to about two months.


[b]The map is running regularily on:[/b]
[i]Mapgate.Eu Jagdrevier [195.13.62.36:27800][/i]



Lastly, it's not limited to GG - there are buyzones and even a secret room full of weapons above the kitchen. Try reaching them before the enemy team does!
